Chat Server implemetation
1. Front end REST API
2. Chat Server 

Real world implementation
Large scale Erlang based XMPP server (facebook implementation)
GCM is also XMPP server (google implementation)

Data Store:
Ideally use Cassandra High Write Store. If sharded by creation time good for querying but issue when storing not load balanced well. 

Currently using MongoDB for ease of implementation
Original My SQL Tables

User
<User Name><User Login> <User Id>

Group
<GroupName>, <GroupID>

Contacts
<UserId> <GroupId> <ContactId>

LoginDetails

MessageDetails


